\fs36 \cf0 What This Product Is\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 myaircraft.us
\f0\b0  is a multi-tenant SaaS platform for aviation maintenance organizations, aircraft owners, and FBOs. It digitizes paper aircraft records, extracts structured data via a multi-engine AI pipeline, and surfaces that data through an AI-powered Q&A system, work orders, compliance tracking, and a mobile scanner workflow.\

